      "title": "Protesters storm into President\u2019s House in Colombo",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Protesters in Colombo Fort, who broke through police barricades to reach the entrance of the President\u2019s House, have stormed into the premises, Ada Derana correspondent says.",
        "According to reports, the police also fired tear gas to disperse the protesters at the Janadhipathi Mawatha."
